-- J&J to Explore Options for Its Ortho Clinical Diagnostics Unit
-- B y   B r u c e   R u l e
-- 2013-01-22T14:29:44Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-01-22/j-j-to-explore-options-for-its-ortho-clinical-diagnostics-unit.html
Johnson & Johnson (JNJ)  will review
options for its Ortho Clinical Diagnostics business, which may
include selling off the unit.  “At this time it is not certain that any transaction will
be consummated,” the New Brunswick, New Jersey-based company
said in a statement today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
